{"tid":507573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得po下面嗰個留言熱門同埋分享嗰個掣掉轉左好麻煩","createTime":"2017-12-23T11:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T11:46:18.000Z","uid":66965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3136bcd7b041fb80e299ffbb63602341e6e72c89","tid":507573,"uid":66965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/23/194002_9413e1b9c49fe0ef87382ed7f91ec457.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F23%2F194002_9413e1b9c49fe0ef87382ed7f91ec457.jpeg&h=a77cdb6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢而家熱門嗰個掣同分享嗰個掣掉轉左<br />\n之前想撳熱門睇留言嘅時候撳慣咗個位<br />\n而家掉轉左成日唔小心撳到分享個位<br />\n搞到成件事好麻煩<br />\n可唔可以調返轉佢啊大佬"}]}